(23, 2, '2005-09-14 17:35:29', '2005-09-14 16:35:29', 'If you have any comments or would like to blog your work at Interactive Architecture dot Org then leave me a message below or <a href="mailto:ruairiglynn@gmail.com">click here to email</a><br /><br />I am currently adding my portfolio to this page so please excuse the mess that this page will be in till I''m finished.<br /><br /><a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/signallers.html">''Signallers''</a>&nbsp; - (Work in Progress)<br />Interactive Architecture Workshop <br />London - 2006<br />Bartlett School of Architecture<br /><br /><a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/angels.html">''Angels'' - Constructing Reconfigurable Space</a><br />Interactive Architecture Workshop <br />London - 2006<br />Bartlett School of Architecture<br /><br /><a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/makinganecology.html">''''Making an Ecology''</a><br />Interactive Architecture Workshop <br />Supported by the EPSRC &amp; Betty Layward School<br />London - 2006<br />Bartlett School of Architecture<br /><br /><a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/reciprocalspace.html">''Reciprocal Space''</a><br />MediaLab Arts<br />Institute of Digital Art &amp; Technology<br />Plymouth - 2005<br />Europrix Top Talent Award Quality Seal<br />Submerge Innovation Award 1st Place<br /><br />''<a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/researchspaces.html">Research Spaces</a>'' <br />Materialization of Practice in Art &amp; Architecture Exhibiition <br />London&nbsp; - 2005 - Collaboration with Paul Burres<br /><br /><a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/clave.html">''C.L.A.V.E.'' - Collaborative Live Audio Virtual Environment </a><br />MediaLab Arts<br />Institute of Digital Art &amp; Technology<br />Plymouth - 2005<br /><br /><a href="http://www.interactivearchitecture.org/portfolio/archive/ripmixburn">''RIP MIX BURN'' Cultural Industries Rede